title: Marilyn Manson - Sweet Dreams CD Single
description:
This is the CD single of "Sweet Dreams (Are Made Of This)" which is of course Marilyn Manson&#039;s cover of a Eurhythmics tune. This CD single contains an edit of "Sweet Dreams" clocking in at 4:25 its a 28 seconds shorter than the LP version as well as two otherwise unavailable B-side tracks. Hope you like it.

1. Sweet Dreams (Are Made Of This) [Single Edit]
2. Dance Of The Dope Hats [Remix]
3. Down In The Park [Gary Numan cover]
4. Lunchbox (Next Motherfucker) [Remix]
